text: Alatana () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Alataninsky Selsoviet, Sterlitamaksky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 137 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 26 km from Sterlitamak. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlitamaksky District
title: Alatana
